Tastygallery - an AJAX image gallery

INSTALLATION
	Simply upload everything to a directory of your choice.
	
CONFIGURATION
	There are a few user-configurable options, such as:
		- Default number of images per row
		- Thumbnail ratio
		- Thumbnail quality
		- Thumbnail directories
	These can be changed at the top of the following files:
		- _tastygallery/js/site.js
		- _tastygallery/common.php

